# meta-display-image

Yocto BSP layers for various board + display combinations composed by Display Image - <https://www.display-image.com>.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============
* URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  * branch: master
  * revision: HEAD



Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-display-image layer to the the maintainers:

Maintainer: j-gre <jan.greiner@mnet-mail.de><jan.greiner@display-image.com>

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-display-image layer to your build
 II. Testing


I. Adding the meta-display-image layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-display-image'

II. Testing
========

This BSP is being tested on a verdin imx8mm with the meta-toradex-torizon <https://github.com/toradex/meta-toradex-torizon> as a base layer.